Description: We have developed and are ready to market the first true mini cloud pc called the KloudPC.
Headquarters Regions: Tampa Bay Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: We have developed and are ready to market the first true mini cloud pc called the KloudPC.  This device in a nutshell is really a tablet that has been converted to a workstation.  It has no moving parts, no fan, no hard drive and is based on the Linux operating system.  Very much like the same technologies that goes into your Smart Phone and Tablet.  This is simply the Workstation PC that now integrates the things you carry around with you to your Desktop.  Since the device stores everything in the cloud you don't need to worry about losing your data should the device fail.  The device is simply replaced and you are back up and running.  The technology has been submitted for a patent and now has a Patent Pending status.
